Any Video Converter Ultimate is an application that you can use to encode video clips of multiple formats (including MOV, MP4, DVDs and MKV) to others (e.g. MP4, WMA, AVI, SWF, FLV).

In the queue you can check out the name, duration, format, frame size, frames per second and status of each video. Once you set the destination format and directory, you can initiate the encoding task.

In addition, you can modify options regarding DVDs (e.g. chapters, audio language, subtitles) and video length (i.e. you can split the clip by marking the start and end time).
